{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":737,"text":"I would like to show you how"},{"time":3646,"text":"architecture has helped"},{"time":6523,"text":"to change the life of my community"},{"time":9618,"text":"and has opened opportunities to hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14433,"text":"I am a native of Burkina Faso."},{"time":17392,"text":"According to the World Bank, Burkina Faso"},{"time":20610,"text":"is one of the poorest countries in the world,"},{"time":23659,"text":"but what does it look like"},{"time":26506,"text":"to grow up in a place like that?"},{"time":29925,"text":"I am an example of that."},{"time":32485,"text":"I was born in a little village called Gando."},{"time":36393,"text":"In Gando, there was no electricity,"},{"time":40885,"text":"no access to clean drinking water, and no school."},{"time":45099,"text":"But my father wanted me"},{"time":47923,"text":"to learn how to read and write."},{"time":49972,"text":"For this reason, I had to leave my family"},{"time":54020,"text":"when I was seven and to stay in a city"},{"time":57914,"text":"far away from my village"},{"time":59902,"text":"with no contact with my family."},{"time":63579,"text":"In this place I sat"},{"time":67000,"text":"in a class like that"},{"time":69226,"text":"with more than 150 other kids,"},{"time":72978,"text":"and for six years."},{"time":75470,"text":"In this time, it just happened to me to come to school"},{"time":79550,"text":"to realize that my classmate died."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85245,"text":"Today, not so much has changed."},{"time":89758,"text":"There is still no electricity in my village."},{"time":94211,"text":"People still are dying in Burkina Faso,"},{"time":96673,"text":"and access to clean drinking water"},{"time":100276,"text":"is still a big problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104499,"text":"I had luck. I was lucky, because this is a fact of life"},{"time":112051,"text":"when you grow up in a place like that."},{"time":114803,"text":"But I was lucky."},{"time":117172,"text":"I had a scholarship."},{"time":119256,"text":"I could go to Germany to study."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123466,"text":"So now, I suppose,"},{"time":127371,"text":"I don't need to explain to you how great a privilege"},{"time":132045,"text":"it is for me to be standing before you today."},{"time":136502,"text":"From Gando, my home village in Burkina Faso,"},{"time":140874,"text":"to Berlin in Germany to become an architect"},{"time":145180,"text":"is a big, big step."},{"time":150345,"text":"But what to do with this privilege?"},{"time":155997,"text":"Since I was a student, I wanted to open up"},{"time":159952,"text":"better opportunities to other kids in Gando."},{"time":162595,"text":"I just wanted to use my skills and build a school."},{"time":165510,"text":"But how do you do it when you're still a student"},{"time":168494,"text":"and you don't have money?"},{"time":170576,"text":"Oh yes, I started to make drawings"},{"time":173078,"text":"and asked for money."},{"time":175060,"text":"Fundraising was not an easy task."},{"time":179039,"text":"I even asked my classmates"},{"time":181838,"text":"to spend less money on coffee and cigarettes,"},{"time":185016,"text":"but to sponsor my school project."},{"time":188984,"text":"In real wonder, two years later,"},{"time":192000,"text":"I was able to collect 50,000 U.S. dollars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198534,"text":"When I came home to Gando"},{"time":201497,"text":"to bring the good news,"},{"time":203022,"text":"my people were over the moon,"},{"time":207171,"text":"but when they realized"},{"time":209792,"text":"that I was planning to use clay,"},{"time":212636,"text":"they were shocked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214719,"text":"\"A clay building is not able to stand a rainy season,"},{"time":218262,"text":"and Francis wants us to use it and build a school."},{"time":223371,"text":"Is this the reason why he spent so much time"},{"time":226135,"text":"in Europe studying"},{"time":228148,"text":"instead of working in the field with us?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":232247,"text":"My people build all the time with clay,"},{"time":236540,"text":"but they don't see any innovation with mud."},{"time":241461,"text":"So I had to convince everybody."},{"time":243650,"text":"I started to speak with the community,"},{"time":247033,"text":"and I could convince everybody,"},{"time":249496,"text":"and we could start to work."},{"time":252506,"text":"And the women, the men,"},{"time":254270,"text":"everybody from the village,"},{"time":256315,"text":"was part of this building process."},{"time":258332,"text":"I was allowed to use even traditional techniques."},{"time":262041,"text":"So clay floor for example,"},{"time":264204,"text":"the young men come and stand like that, beating,"},{"time":268600,"text":"hours for hours,"},{"time":270196,"text":"and then their mothers came,"},{"time":271908,"text":"and they are beating in this position,"},{"time":275642,"text":"for hours, giving water and beating."},{"time":280258,"text":"And then the polishers come."},{"time":281886,"text":"They start polishing it with a stone for hours."},{"time":286944,"text":"And then you have this result,"},{"time":291901,"text":"very fine, like a baby bottom."},{"time":295210,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":296983,"text":"It's not photoshopped. (Laughter)"},{"time":302248,"text":"This is the school, built with the community."},{"time":305232,"text":"The walls are totally made out"},{"time":307022,"text":"of compressed clay blocks from Gando."},{"time":311122,"text":"The roof structure is made"},{"time":314276,"text":"with cheap steel bars"},{"time":317098,"text":"normally hiding inside concrete."},{"time":320994,"text":"And the classroom, the ceiling is made"},{"time":324062,"text":"out of both of them used together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326817,"text":"In this school, there was a simple idea:"},{"time":329727,"text":"to create comfort in a classroom."},{"time":333437,"text":"Don't forget, it can be 45 degrees in Burkina Faso,"},{"time":338608,"text":"so with simple ventilation,"},{"time":340542,"text":"I wanted to make the classroom"},{"time":342592,"text":"good for teaching and learning."},{"time":345201,"text":"And this is the project today,"},{"time":348046,"text":"12 years old, still in best condition."},{"time":351680,"text":"And the kids, they love it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357936,"text":"And for me and my community,"},{"time":360791,"text":"this project was a huge success."},{"time":364446,"text":"It has opened up opportunities"},{"time":367348,"text":"to do more projects in Gando."},{"time":369939,"text":"So I could do a lot of projects,"},{"time":372877,"text":"and here I am going to share with you"},{"time":375201,"text":"only three of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377381,"text":"The first one is the school extension, of course."},{"time":381177,"text":"How do you explain drawings and engineering"},{"time":384492,"text":"to people who are neither able to read nor write?"},{"time":388144,"text":"I started to build a prototype like that."},{"time":391091,"text":"The innovation was to build a clay vault."},{"time":394077,"text":"So then, I jumped on the top like that,"},{"time":397408,"text":"with my team, and it works."},{"time":399720,"text":"The community is looking. It still works."},{"time":401947,"text":"So we can build. (Laughter)"},{"time":404805,"text":"And we kept building, and that is the result."},{"time":408688,"text":"The kids are happy, and they love it."},{"time":412322,"text":"The community is very proud. We made it."},{"time":416483,"text":"And even animals, like these donkeys,"},{"time":420624,"text":"love our buildings."},{"time":422384,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":426031,"text":"The next project is the library in Gando."},{"time":430698,"text":"And see now, we tried to introduce"},{"time":434361,"text":"different ideas in our buildings,"},{"time":436876,"text":"but we often don't have so much material."},{"time":440707,"text":"Something we have in Gando are clay pots."},{"time":444110,"text":"We wanted to use them to create openings."},{"time":447431,"text":"So we just bring them like you can see"},{"time":449541,"text":"to the building site."},{"time":451967,"text":"we start cutting them,"},{"time":454133,"text":"and then we place them on top of the roof"},{"time":457064,"text":"before we pour the concrete,"},{"time":459643,"text":"and you have this result."},{"time":461654,"text":"The openings are letting the hot air out"},{"time":464564,"text":"and light in."},{"time":466403,"text":"Very simple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468476,"text":"My most recent project in Gando"},{"time":471314,"text":"is a high school project."},{"time":473332,"text":"I would like to share with you this."},{"time":475265,"text":"The innovation in this project"},{"time":477510,"text":"is to cast mud like you cast concrete."},{"time":482253,"text":"How do you cast mud?"},{"time":484378,"text":"We start making a lot of mortars, like you can see,"},{"time":487644,"text":"and when everything is ready,"},{"time":489767,"text":"when you know what is the best recipe"},{"time":491904,"text":"and the best form,"},{"time":493098,"text":"you start working with the community."},{"time":495749,"text":"And sometimes I can leave."},{"time":497895,"text":"They will do it themselves."},{"time":499654,"text":"I came to speak to you like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503206,"text":"Another factor in Gando is rain."},{"time":505897,"text":"When the rains come,"},{"time":507721,"text":"we hurry up to protect our fragile walls"},{"time":510009,"text":"against the rain."},{"time":513061,"text":"Don't confound with Christo and Jeanne-Claude."},{"time":516573,"text":"It is simply how we protect our walls."},{"time":519138,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":520607,"text":"The rain in Burkina comes very fast,"},{"time":523485,"text":"and after that, you have floods"},{"time":526050,"text":"everywhere in the country."},{"time":528995,"text":"But for us, the rain is good."},{"time":532045,"text":"It brings sand and gravel to the river"},{"time":535950,"text":"we need to use to build."},{"time":538221,"text":"We just wait for the rain to go."},{"time":540122,"text":"We take the sand, we mix it with clay,"},{"time":543716,"text":"and we keep building."},{"time":546502,"text":"That is it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":548307,"text":"The Gando project was always\nconnected to training the people,"},{"time":551401,"text":"because I just wanted, one day"},{"time":554893,"text":"when I fall down and die,"},{"time":557796,"text":"that at least one person from Gando"},{"time":560480,"text":"keeps doing this work."},{"time":564222,"text":"But you will be surprised. I'm still alive."},{"time":567065,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":568615,"text":"And my people now can use their skills"},{"time":571792,"text":"to earn money themselves."},{"time":576830,"text":"Usually, for a young man from Gando to earn money,"},{"time":580793,"text":"you have to leave the country"},{"time":582889,"text":"to the city, sometimes leave the country"},{"time":586132,"text":"and some never come back,"},{"time":588124,"text":"making the community weaker."},{"time":591568,"text":"But now they can stay in the country"},{"time":595245,"text":"and work on different building sites"},{"time":597437,"text":"and earn money to feed their family."},{"time":599324,"text":"There's a new quality in this work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604278,"text":"Yes, you know it."},{"time":606474,"text":"I have won a lot of awards through this work."},{"time":611128,"text":"For sure, it has opened opportunities."},{"time":614809,"text":"I have become myself known."},{"time":617201,"text":"But the reason why I do what I do"},{"time":622091,"text":"is my community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625566,"text":"When I was a kid,"},{"time":627680,"text":"I was going to school,"},{"time":629463,"text":"I was coming back every holiday to Gando."},{"time":633494,"text":"By the end of every holidays,"},{"time":635637,"text":"I had to say goodbye to the community,"},{"time":638681,"text":"going from one compound to another one."},{"time":642427,"text":"All women in Gando will open their clothes like that"},{"time":647658,"text":"and give me the last penny."},{"time":651593,"text":"In my culture, this is a symbol of deep affection."},{"time":656714,"text":"As a seven-year-old guy, I was impressed."},{"time":659897,"text":"I just asked my mother one day,"},{"time":662487,"text":"\"Why do all these women love me so much?\""},{"time":665230,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":666979,"text":"She just answered,"},{"time":669314,"text":"\"They are contributing to pay for your education"},{"time":673095,"text":"hoping that you will be successful"},{"time":676440,"text":"and one day come back and help"},{"time":679538,"text":"improve the quality of life of the community.\""},{"time":683570,"text":"I hope now that I was able\nto make my community proud"},{"time":688448,"text":"through this work,"},{"time":690321,"text":"and I hope I was able to prove you the power"},{"time":694133,"text":"of community,"},{"time":695772,"text":"and to show you that architecture"},{"time":699499,"text":"can be inspiring for communities"},{"time":704188,"text":"to shape their own future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706441,"text":"Merci beaucoup. (Applause)"},{"time":708828,"text":"Thank you. Thank you. Thank you. Thank you."},{"time":713169,"text":"Thank you. Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}